nl: 對於每一支贏得過C組賽車的隊伍，請告訴我他們是否也曾贏得過D組比賽？請按字母順序列出這些隊伍。
sql:
SELECT DISTINCT
  T1.`Group C Winner` AS `Team`,
  CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
      SELECT
        1
      FROM
        `table_1_1137142_1`
      WHERE
        `Group D Winner` = T1.`Group C Winner`
    )
    THEN `Also Won Group D`
    ELSE `Never Won Group D`
  END AS `Status`
FROM
  `table_1_1137142_1` AS T1
ORDER BY
